    alarmActiveTable  OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      SEQUENCE OF    AlarmActiveRecord
        MAX-ACCESS  not-accessible
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Table with one record for each Alarms&Controls that is active in
